    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This vehicle is a true collector-grade specimen, meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled environment. The exterior features original factory paint with a deep, mirror-like luster, protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating\u2014absolutely zero swirl marks, chips, or dings. Inside, the cabin remains in showroom condition; the premium leather upholstery is supple with no signs of wear, and the dashboard is pristine. Mechanically, it is flawless, having undergone every scheduled service at the dealership with a comprehensive paper trail to prove it. Every electronic component and driver-assist feature functions perfectly. It drives exactly as it did the day it left the lot, offering a tight, responsive experience. This is as close to a brand-new car as you can find on the pre-owned market.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
